{"tid":2147390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Starlink 衛星寬頻需求超大  用戶終端增至500萬、年底開始商業服務","createTime":"2020-08-09T08:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T16:49:34.000Z","uid":105678,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3290905880c4f598b88aeb52f4fbbbecfb9cde8e","tid":2147390,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/106643649-1596306106356-zy2ypdy6pta51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F106643649-1596306106356-zy2ypdy6pta51.jpg&h=607a789f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前報道過 SpaceX 研發「星鏈計劃」 (Starlink)，希望把高速寬頻網絡服務覆蓋至偏遠地區等的用戶；近日 SpaceX 考慮到需求高於預期的問題，決定向官方提出更多申請。<br />\n<br />\n在上月 31 日 SpaceX 向美國聯邦通信委員會（FCC）提出申請，要求把碟形衛星用戶終端（user terminal）的授權數量從原本 100 萬個增加至 500 萬個。SpaceX 對 FCC 表示，Starlink 今年底就會在美國北部及加拿大南部提供商業服務，2021 年衛星網路服務涵蓋範圍會迅速拓展至全球。<br />\n<br />\nElon Musk 日前也透過 Twitter 表示，Starlink 衛星地面站內建馬達，能自行轉到最適合的角度，不需要專家安裝。只要插上電、放在清楚看到天空之處即可；你可以放在花園、屋頂、桌子上，任何地方都可以，重點是須看到大片天空。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/105931058-1558669544709starlinkdeployment.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F105931058-1558669544709starlinkdeployment.jpg&h=c12d085b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截至 6 月中，SpaceX 已發射 540 顆 Starlink 衛星，並從當時開始邀請支持者加入其他測試計劃，公眾測試隨後也會開始；相信 Starlink 將打造由 12000 顆近地軌道小型衛星組成的低成本互聯網。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：CNBC"},{"pid":"aad119b7fa65bb67737e808260649f7de8ff9c26","tid":2147390,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"壞咗點維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb697e079d9924beb820ffdf395e36a423449f9","tid":2147390,"uid":271756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aad119b7fa65bb67737e808260649f7de8ff9c26","tid":2147390,"uid":77134,"like":0,"